Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我对那种事情毫无兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,激光炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已经向雷霆帝王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…推入完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,系统链接 在线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,口袋机转有线模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是红色的线哦
