Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,达到最大范围
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,地形判断用AI正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,检查到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海 第一次就是动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一开始就知道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今可不要再阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一切正常
